{"id":"leg003","type":"text","x":2324,"y":498,"width":432,"height":270,"angle":0,"strokeColor":"#334155","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"groupIds":[],"roundness":null,"seed":7003,"version":1,"versionNonce":7003,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":[],"updated":1747440000000,"index":"cE","link":null,"locked":false,"frameId":null,"text":"Green ellipse ⬤   = Start / End (login or done)\nBlue rect  ■       = FE page / UI action\nOrange rect ■    = API call (BE endpoint)\nPurple rect ■    = Realtime connection (SSE/WS)\nAmber diamond ◆ = Decision / branch\nGreen rect ■     = Success / auto status update\nRed rect ■        = Error path (cancel, reject)\n\n─────────────────────────────────────────\nSOLID arrow  ───►  = intra-actor flow (within lane)\nDASHED cyan  - - ►  = WS event (broadcast to staff)\nDASHED purple - - ► = SSE event (broadcast to customer)\n─────────────────────────────────────────\nLane order = auth hierarchy:\nguest < chef = cashier < staff < manager < admin","fontSize":11,"fontFamily":2,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","containerId":null,"originalText":"Green ellipse ⬤   = Start / End (login or done)\nBlue rect  ■       = FE page / UI action\nOrange rect ■    = API call (BE endpoint)\nPurple rect ■    = Realtime connection (SSE/WS)\nAmber diamond ◆ = Decision / branch\nGreen rect ■     = Success / auto status update\nRed rect ■        = Error path (cancel, reject)\n\n─────────────────────────────────────────\nSOLID arrow  ───►  = intra-actor flow (within lane)\nDASHED cyan  - - ►  = WS event (broadcast to staff)\nDASHED purple - - ► = SSE event (broadcast to customer)\n─────────────────────────────────────────\nLane order = auth hierarchy:\nguest < chef = cashier < staff < manager < admin","lineHeight":1.35,"autoResize":false},
{"id":"note001","type":"rectangle","x":2310,"y":816,"width":460,"height":160,"angle":0,"strokeColor":"#d97706","backgroundColor":"#fffbeb","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"dashed","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"groupIds":[],"roundness":{"type":3},"seed":7010,"version":1,"versionNonce":7010,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":[],"updated":1747440000000,"index":"cF","link":null,"locked":false,"frameId":null},
{"id":"note002","type":"text","x":2324,"y":826,"width":432,"height":140,"angle":0,"strokeColor":"#92400e","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"groupIds":[],"roundness":null,"seed":7011,"version":1,"versionNonce":7011,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":[],"updated":1747440000000,"index":"cG","link":null,"locked":false,"frameId":null,"text":"KEY BUSINESS RULES\n\n• 1 table = max 1 active order (409 if duplicate)\n• Guest JWT: stateless, 2h exp, no refresh\n• Cancel: only if qty_served < 30% of total\n• Payment: only if order.status = ready\n• Combo: backend expands → sub-items for KDS\n• WS events: Redis PubSub → all subscribed clients\n• SSE: exponential backoff reconnect (1s→30s max)","fontSize":11,"fontFamily":2,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","containerId":null,"originalText":"KEY BUSINESS RULES\n\n• 1 table = max 1 active order (409 if duplicate)\n• Guest JWT: stateless, 2h exp, no refresh\n• Cancel: only if qty_served < 30% of total\n• Payment: only if order.status = ready\n• Combo: backend expands → sub-items for KDS\n• WS events: Redis PubSub → all subscribed clients\n• SSE: exponential backoff reconnect (1s→30s max)","lineHeight":1.35,"autoResize":false},
